span> 标题：比加（beqa）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：בֶּקַע</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：beqa‘)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:22\">GEN 24:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:26\">EXO 38:26</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>根据<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:26\">EXO 38:26</a> ，<em>beqa‘</em> （比加）为半舍客勒。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:22\">GEN 24:22</a> 指出这是一个金鼻环的重量。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Revised Standard Version (1989)\">NRSV</abbr> 将其换算为舍客勒，英文意为“一个重半舍客勒的金鼻环”。1比加等于10季拉。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
